sequenceDiagram
%% Sequence Diagram Example - Trimble Theme
%%
%% Theme Impact:
%% - Actors (participant boxes): actorBkg (#0063A3 Trimble Blue) with white text
%% - Actor borders: actorBorder (#004F83 light / #89C6ED dark)
%% - Lifelines: actorLineColor (#585C65 light / #A3A6B1 dark)
%% - Messages/arrows: signalColor with textColor for labels
%% - Activation bars: activationBkgColor (#C7E2F6 light / #0E416C dark)
%% - Notes: noteBkgColor (#FFF5E4 cream light / #464B52 gray dark) with Gold border
%% - Alt/Loop boxes: labelBoxBkgColor (#DCEDF9 light / #003054 dark)
%% - Sequence numbers: sequenceNumberColor (#FFFFFF) on Blue background
%% - Layout: actorMargin 50px, messageMargin 35px, mirrorActors enabled
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant C as Client App
    participant A as API Gateway
    participant S as Auth Service
    participant D as Database

    U->>C: Click Login
    C->>A: POST /auth/login
    A->>S: Validate Credentials
    S->>D: Query User
    D-->>S: User Data
    alt Valid User
        S-->>A: JWT Token
        A-->>C: 200 OK + Token
        C-->>U: Redirect to Dashboard
    else Invalid User
        S-->>A: Authentication Failed
        A-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
        C-->>U: Show Error Message
    end

    Note over U,C: User is now authenticated
    U->>C: Request Protected Resource
    C->>A: GET /api/data (with JWT)
    A->>S: Verify Token
    S-->>A: Token Valid
    A->>D: Fetch Data
    D-->>A: Data Response
    A-->>C: 200 OK + Data
    C-->>U: Display Data
